name: Cantemo.GitHub.io
body:
### Welcome to Cantemo GitHub repository.

We have a number of example Apps, plugins and code associated with Cantemo Portal.

### [Extra Item Page Information](https://github.com/Cantemo/Extra-ItemPage-Information-Example)
See how to create a very small App that will add some extra information on the Item Page for video and sequence items.

### Support or Contact
Please contact your local reseller for more information and on how to get help on this.
